1	acid-arrow	Acid Arrow	90 feet	powdered rhubarb leaf	f	Instantaneous	f	Action	2		{"name": "Evocation"}	{"A shimmering green arrow streaks toward a target","within range and bursts in a spray of acid. Make a","ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the","target takes 4d4 Acid damage and 2d4 Acid dam-","age at the end of its next turn. On a miss, the arrow","splashes the target with acid for half as much of the","initial damage only."}	{"Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot. The damage","(both initial and later) increases by 1d4 for each","spell slot level above 2."}	{V,S,M}	{"2": ["4d4 Acid", "2d4 Acid"], "3": ["5d4 Acid", "3d4 Acid"], "4": ["6d4 Acid", "4d4 Acid"], "5": ["7d4 Acid", "5d4 Acid"], "6": ["8d4 Acid", "6d4 Acid"], "7": ["9d4 Acid", "7d4 Acid"], "8": ["10d4 Acid", "8d4 Acid"], "9": ["11d4 Acid", "9d4 Acid"]}	/api/spells/acid-arrow	2026-02-19 17:55:29.509433
