r smaller), 2d6 + 3 + your spellcasting","ability modifier (Large), or 2d12 + 3 + your spellcasting","ability modifier (Huge)."}	{"Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot. The creature’s","Slam damage increases by 1d4 (Medium or smaller),","1d6 (Large), or 1d12 (Huge) for each spell slot level","above 5."}	{V,S}	[]	/api/spells/animate-objects	2026-02-19 17:55:29.571879
