target has the Poisoned","condition until the start of the insect’s next turn."}	{"Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot. Use the spell","slot’s level for the spell’s level in the stat block."}	{V,S}	[]	/api/spells/giant-insect	2026-02-19 17:55:30.173753
