294	spiritual-weapon	Spiritual Weapon	60 feet		f	Concentration, up to 1 minute	t	Bonus Action	2		{"name": "Evocation"}	{"You create a floating, spectral force that resembles","a weapon of your choice and lasts for the duration.","The force appears within range in a space of your","choice, and you can immediately make one melee","spell attack against one creature within 5 feet of the","force. On a hit, the target takes Force damage equal","to 1d8 plus your spellcasting ability modifier.","As a Bonus Action on your later turns, you can","move the force up to 20 feet and repeat the attack","against a creature within 5 feet of it."}	{"Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot. The damage in-","creases by 1d8 for every slot level above 2."}	{V,S}	[]	/api/spells/spiritual-weapon	2026-02-19 17:55:30.843199
