297	stone-shape	Stone Shape	Touch	soft clay	f	Instantaneous	f	Action	4		{"name": "Transmutation"}	{"You touch a stone object of Medium size or smaller","or a section of stone no more than 5 feet in any di-","mension and form it into any shape you like. For ex-","ample, you could shape a large rock into a weapon,","statue, or coffer, or you could make a small passage","through a wall that is 5 feet thick. You could also","shape a stone door or its frame to seal the door shut.","The object you create can have up to two hinges and","a latch, but finer mechanical detail isn’t possible."}	{}	{V,S,M}	[]	/api/spells/stone-shape	2026-02-19 17:55:30.855841
